  "2122880": {
    "name": "左左和右右：手拉手！",
    "steam_appid": 2122880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/a274e2a306ae80f6a7794277bc941a23.avif?t=1768496452\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras_big/a274e2a306ae80f6a7794277bc941a23.webp?t=1768496452 width=1560 height=504 /></span><strong>一起扮演左手和右手吧！ </strong><br> 在这个充满趣味和温馨的双人合作冒险中，托儿所里的所有毛绒玩具都不见了！你将扮演孩子们的双手，在他们的幻想世界中寻找毛茸茸的小伙伴。你能找出是谁或什么引发了这场奇怪的事件吗？跳跃、剪切、抓取、拳击和击掌，一路闯过充满谜题、秘密和挑战的三个世界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>手拉手！</strong><br>体验一场充满趣味的双人合作冒险，你和朋友互相帮忙，共同前进。不管是本地游玩还是通过远端同乐，都可以用键盘和手柄或两个手柄体验，无需分屏！<strong>注意：部分位于中国大陆的玩家在使用线上模式时，可能会遇到延迟或断线问题。我们正在持续改进亚洲地区的网络体验。如果连接不稳定，建议使用 Steam 远端同乐，只需一份游戏，就能与好友轻松同乐！而普通线上联机则需要两份游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/701db10b4c0587236b69621b92cca73b.poster.avif?t=1768496452\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/701db10b4c0587236b69621b92cca73b.webm?t=1768496452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/701db10b4c0587236b69621b92cca73b.mp4?t=1768496452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>灵巧操控！</strong><br>你的身体让你能在这些奇幻世界中互动。用“石头”可以拳击障碍物，变成“纸”可以抓取物品和击掌！当然，“剪刀”用来剪开前路也必不可少！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/1c42d0ca7ac9c9496bfbf5ace767f6a9.poster.avif?t=1768496452\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/1c42d0ca7ac9c9496bfbf5ace767f6a9.webm?t=1768496452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/1c42d0ca7ac9c9496bfbf5ace767f6a9.mp4?t=1768496452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作工具！</strong><br>在这些世界中，你可以找到各种工具，比如“伸缩手臂”用来够高处，“橡皮筋”能让你们变成弹弓，或是混合颜料穿过色块。大多数工具还可以组合使用！利用它们来救出所有失踪的毛绒玩具吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/f6de59d8464333f54a6f957713581b94.poster.avif?t=1768496452\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/f6de59d8464333f54a6f957713581b94.webm?t=1768496452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122880/extras/f6de59d8464333f54a6f957713581b94.mp4?t=1768496452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定制触手可及！</strong><br>每个世界中隐藏着许多秘密、装饰品和额外挑战。购买外观饰品，跳上颜料管改变外形。你能全部找到吗？</p></li></ul>",
